window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Previously published as <i>Desperate Times: The Complete Edition</i> <i>(An EMP Apocalypse Survival Harem)</i> by Lara X. Lust (author).</p> <p><b>Adapt. Survive. Sustain.</b></p> <p><i>The entire Desperate Times trilogy in one collection with a new epilogue!</i></p> <p>Dom’s life was never easy.</p> <p>Forged in the fires of poverty and neglect, he’s spent years building a life for himself. And it seems like everything is finally coming together. He lives on his own in a decent house at the edge of town, he works for himself, he’s debt-free, and, most recently, his relationship with his attractive best friend seems to be heading somewhere....</p> <p>But everything is about to change.</p> <p>When a catastrophic solar flare fries the electric grid, Dom and the two women he cares about most will be forced to walk hundreds of miles through chaos to a safe location. Bad weather, dangerous people, and a world gone crazy stand between them and sanctuary.</p> <p>It will take everything everything for them to survive.</p>"; 
